  "short_description": "Intel AX210 WiFi 6E and BT5 module, PCIe ×1 interface, ARS-WiFi6E-M2 Tri-band Panel 5dBi Antenna",
  "description": "Intel AX210 WiFi 6E and BT5 module, PCIe ×1 interface, ARS-WiFi6E-M2 Tri-band Panel 5dBi Antenna",
  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Description",
      "text": "The AIT-AX210-EZ is a WiFi 6E and Bluetooth 5 PCIe card based on the Intel AX210 module, designed for desktop PCs with a PCIe ×1 interface. It is equipped with ARS-WiFi6E-M2 tri-band panel 4dBi antenna with 2m long LMR-100 RF cable."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Description",
      "text": "AIT-AX210-EZ supports the latest WiFi 6E (IEEE 802.11ax) with special features like OFDMA, 1024QAM and MU-MIMO. Module includes also Bluetooth 5.2, is backward compatible and operates in 2.4, 5 and 6 GHz bands."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Description",
      "text": "AIT-AX210-EZ card has PCIe ×1 interface, which allows using this set in any desktop PC equipped with PCIe ×1, ×4, ×8 or ×16 slot."
    }
  ],
